data.description: Ranch Style home with Golf Views and spacious RV Garage. Walk to the clubhouse for drinks or dinner no membership required. Some of the best features in the area. Remodeled kitchen with additional covered Patio, has a commercial grade 6 burner stainless steel Wolf stove, granite counter tops, and Brazilian hardwood floors. Travertine stone tile in the bathrooms . Special touches, including plantation shutters, wood trim, and a gas fireplace, make this home comfortable and inviting. A large laundry/utility room, formal dining area  add great usefulness to the floor plan. Mountain and Fairway views from the fully landscaped and fenced back yard, with huge mature trees for shade and includes solar. HOA Dues are voluntary.
